>\n唔出馬路，唔塞通道，手拖手企係行人路<br />\n如果聽到有熟悉既歌曲(如Do you hear the people sing, Sing hallelujah to the Lord, 海闊天空，光輝歲月等)就加入啦~<br />\n各位注意安全，參加者和平理性非暴力，不作出任何違法行為。遇上重大危險人鏈會解散及離開。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘線義工 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxElY6fbKJUooQCgUZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3VqxElY6fbKJUooQCgUZA&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=e970a9d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxElY6fbKJUooQCgUZA</a><br />\n港島線義工 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBfGmB3J_KpqcSwu6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3VqxBfGmB3J_KpqcSwu6A&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=9eebedf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBfGmB3J_KpqcSwu6A</a><br />\n荃灣線義工 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBNJRH3QOKTm3k1nCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3VqxBNJRH3QOKTm3k1nCQ&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=94921182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBNJRH3QOKTm3k1nCQ</a><br />\n天星小輪 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBNT5ypXrRI58K2_WA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3VqxBNT5ypXrRI58K2_WA&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=f3f4c6c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBNT5ypXrRI58K2_WA</a><br />\n唱歌組 <a href=\"https://t.me/thujeruergurfergaer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fthujeruergurfergaer&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=c662201b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/thujeruergurfergaer</a>"},{"pid":"e63e9d47d6433026bf6c3c5688d447bb5f7246de","tid":1495867,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}